    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个游戏中，你需要击败巨人以获取他们的核心。<br>为此，你可以建造巨大的行走堡垒并为其装备武器。<br>要为这些堡垒提供能量，你需要制造能量立方——但请注意，敌人不会让你轻松获取材料！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>行走堡垒</strong><br>升级你的基地，使其能够行走，甚至飞行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/220f3ecd4f58795031044613f84b7a45.poster.avif?t=1764249778\" width=590 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/220f3ecd4f58795031044613f84b7a45.webm?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/220f3ecd4f58795031044613f84b7a45.mp4?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>巨型 Boss</strong><br>有些 Boss 只有在基地的帮助下才能击败！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/8b071e949ca20616771e90f94eac7087.poster.avif?t=1764249778\" width=590 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/8b071e949ca20616771e90f94eac7087.webm?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/8b071e949ca20616771e90f94eac7087.mp4?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong><br>花时间探索洛亚的广阔世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/4a3bc1fbf0d386bcf39c08470ca78913.poster.avif?t=1764249778\" width=588 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/4a3bc1fbf0d386bcf39c08470ca78913.webm?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/4a3bc1fbf0d386bcf39c08470ca78913.mp4?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>防御塔</strong><br>通过放置自动攻击敌人的防御塔来保护你的基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/ea8dc388e53371441ef4f2b3a7af19a7.poster.avif?t=1764249778\" width=590 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/ea8dc388e53371441ef4f2b3a7af19a7.webm?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/ea8dc388e53371441ef4f2b3a7af19a7.mp4?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造</strong><br>收集资源来打造和升级你的基地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/9fa2d6bac7db38ec493e7963cfecb1b2.poster.avif?t=1764249778\" width=590 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/9fa2d6bac7db38ec493e7963cfecb1b2.webm?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/9fa2d6bac7db38ec493e7963cfecb1b2.mp4?t=1764249778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人游戏</strong><br>和朋友一起进行私人游戏，或加入专用服务器！<br>服务器已优化，可支持多达 25 名玩家！（理论上可以更多，但我没测试过）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>其他特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有程序生成奖励的任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洞穴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下城</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可捕捉/可骑乘的宠物</p></li></ul>",
